319
00:21:35,550 --> 00:21:37,320
Cos to řekl?

320
00:21:40,280 --> 00:21:41,570
Pokud máš odvahu, řekni to znovu.

321
00:21:41,570 --> 00:21:43,220
Qi Ruifengu.

322
00:21:47,010 --> 00:21:50,110
